        Exclusive Listing vs Open Listing in Brisbane: Which Is Right for Your Sale?
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        One agent or many? The choice between an exclusive listing and an open listing affects how your property is marketed, how agents invest their time, and ultimately what you achieve at sale.
      </p>
